{"tid":965320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我是卧底】現職警親述1年無間地獄","createTime":"2019-01-02T03:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T11:55:36.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"567b73a76f9d3744d2aea4cfb2000e92f22e0bbb","tid":965320,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJfcQ8rx2UA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyJfcQ8rx2UA&d=MXhVha7Nm3DnEh1U5ZIZVm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2dc2cedb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJfcQ8rx2UA</a><br />\n<br />\n【兩面不是人】<br />\n【本報訊】《無間道》的陳永仁、《學警狙擊》的Laughing哥，潛行黑白兩道之間，在黑暗人性中接受歷練&hellip;&hellip;這不僅是電影橋段，在現實中經歷卧底生涯一年的現役警員阿成向《蘋果》現身說法，披露潛入黑道期間面對的種種難關，更首度打破外界對卧底的幻想和謎思，解構與操控員（Handler）的溝通方式、見面地點，如何撰寫卧底日記，以至重返警隊後被同袍當作「變節警」的內心掙扎。阿成做卧底期間經常提醒自己：「我係一個警察！」他就是憑着這個堅定信念，完成了不一樣的任務。"},{"pid":"abcc7b8b4cda9f54369b406e937ce9c05d7666fa","tid":965320,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"hi嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43221e08dd53ea3686130835ca6fa1a01bc550c0","tid":965320,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e344d71e3b6e237db682d2f908187c7bccd86b","tid":965320,"uid":129011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"training day"},{"pid":"f0299225ae340a95a17f72a9f9ec56fdcb20edda","tid":965320,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47511ebe98f1c624265e5e6051a098536c444c6d","tid":965320,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2